data.description: YOU REALLY NEED TO SEE THIS HOME!! This Beautiful and Stunning home is in Sunburst Lakes. Being perfectly placed on one of their lakes, just adds to the list of great features!  This lovely, spacious 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath open floor plan boasts brand new architectural roof. The HVAC was installed 2 years ago. A 50yr waterproof luxury vinyl flooring has been installed throughout the entire downstairs, laundry room & even bathrooms! New paint throughout, and cozy new carpet upstairs! As soon as you walk in you are greeted by beautiful wainscoting and a raised granite counter, perfect for some stools. Behind that is your beautiful galley kitchen.  While enjoying a meal in your breakfast nook, drink in the beautiful view overlooking the lake, or walk out onto your patio under your gazebo withsolar lighting to enjoy your morning coffee.  Your kitchen is simply breathtaking with gorgeous granite countertops, deep and wide single sink, and is fully appointed with stainless appliances and new fixtures.  Your crab pot will fit perfectly on the stove underneath because of your new low-profile microwave!  Your main suite upstairs has views of the lake and fountain behind your home. If you open the windows while you sleep and listen to the spectacular fountain, the best dreams are sure to come your way! This spacious suite features cathedral ceilings.  The main suite bath features a separate shower, soaking tub, a large walk-in closet as well as dual sinks and Corian countertops on the vanity. The two supporting bedrooms are also upstairs, along with another full bath. Your spacious detached 2-car garage offers a breezeway from the full front porch. It protects you from the rain whether you are bringing in kids, groceries, or both!  This gorgeous home offers Dorchester District 2 schools of Knightsville Elementary School, Dubose Middle, and Summerville High.  Sunburst Lakes HOA provides a pool, play park, RV storage, trash and recycle pickup, and subscription to the Summerville Journal Scene.  Call today to schedule YOUR tour!
